ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[Most previous outbreaks of norovirus infection have occurred in cruise
ships leaving from North American ports, although in some instances the
infection may have been introduced by cruise passengers arriving by air
from Europe. In the present outbreak on board the Regal Princess, the
infection appears to have been introduced by one or more of the passengers
embarking at Copenhagen. The outbreak appears to have been contained by
early recognition of the problem and implementation of containment
measures. - Mod.CP]
